50:08.506 --> 50:12.419
If it's one person that sees you,
kill him.

50:14.220 --> 50:15.676
Tommy?

50:16.222 --> 50:17.883
Tom: Kill him?

50:18.682 --> 50:21.048
If it's more than one, you run.

50:23.187 --> 50:25.929
Come back when the moon is full,

50:26.106 --> 50:28.563
not the half moon,
not the fingernail moon.

50:29.401 --> 50:32.859
Walk at night. Sleep in the day.

50:33.030 --> 50:36.022
