59:19.806 --> 59:21.846
If someone on the committee's
leaking information...

59:21.975 --> 59:24.387
Nobody's been leaking anything.

59:24.561 --> 59:26.472
At least not to me.

59:26.813 --> 59:31.978
I merely asked myself
what my first priority would be

59:32.110 --> 59:34.066
if I were in your shoes.

59:34.529 --> 59:38.693
The answer, of course, is information.

59:38.867 --> 59:41.153
That means spies.

59:42.245 --> 59:46.158
- Well, we like to call them scouts.
- Okay.

59:46.333 --> 59:48.699
Scouts, by all means.

59:49.461 --> 59:55.707
And each of we scouts
is to be ignorant of the others.

59:55.884 --> 1:00:00.503
In case of capture or torture.

1:00:03.767 --> 1:00:07.305
If you don't think you can make it,
you just say so.

1:00:08.480 --> 1:00:10.095
You're not gonna be
much good to anyone

1:00:10.232 --> 1:00:15.443
lying dead of a heart attack beside
